<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang=en>
    <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <link rel="icon" href="../../../../favicon.ico">

    <title>새로운 모임 :: MOIM</title>
        
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gijgo@1.9.10/js/gijgo.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gijgo@1.9.10/css/gijgo.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />


    <script src="./config/datepicker.kr.js" charset="UTF-8"></script>
        
    <script type='text/javascript'>

    $(function(){

        $('.input-group.date').datepicker({

            calendarWeeks: false,

            todayHighlight: true,

            autoclose: true,

            format: "yyyy/mm/dd",

            language: "kr"

        });

    });

    </script>


    

    <!-- Custom styles for this template -->
    <link href="jumbotron.css" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body>
    <header>
       <% include ./login_header.ejs%>>
    </header>
        
    <main role="main">
        <br><br><br>
		<div class="container">

			<div class="col-sm-8">
		
			    <br><br>
                <h1>새로운 모임 만들기</h1><br>
			
			
			    <form action="/new" method="post" >
			      <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="title">모임명</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="title" required>
                    <div class="invalid-feedback">
                    모임명을 입력해주세요
                    </div>
                 </div>

                  <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="introduction">모임소개</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="introduction" required>
                   <div class="invalid-feedback">
                   모임소개를 입력해주세요
                   </div>
                  </div>
                    
                  <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="keyword">모임주제</label>
                  <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" name="keyword" required>
                      <option value>선택</option>
                      <option>친목</option><option>운동</option><option>스터디</option><option>투자</option><option>코딩</option>
                   <div class="invalid-feedback">
                   모임소개를 입력해주세요
                   </div>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="min_num">최소인원</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="min_num" required>
                   <div class="invalid-feedback">
                   최소인원을 입력해주세요
                   </div>
                  </div>
                    
                     <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="max_num">최대인원</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control" name="max_num" required>
                   <div class="invalid-feedback">
                   최대인원을 입력해주세요
                   </div>
                  </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="location">지역</label>
                  <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" name="location" required>
                      <option value>선택</option>
                      <option>서울시 강남구</option><option>서울시 서대문구</option><option>서울시 은평구</option><option>경기</option><option>제주</option>
                   <div class="invalid-feedback">
                   지역을 입력해주세요
                   </div>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                    
                    <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="start">시작일</label>
        
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input id="start" />
                        <script>
                            $('#start').datepicker({
                                uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4'
                            });
                        </script>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                        
                        <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="finish">종료일</label>
                
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input id="finish" />
                        <script>
                            $('#finish').datepicker({
                                uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4'
                            });
                        </script>  
                    </div>
                </div>
                    
                 <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="start_at">모집 시작일</label>
        
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input id="start_at" />
                        <script>
                            $('#start_at').datepicker({
                                uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4'
                            });
                        </script>                              
                    </div>
                </div>
                        
                        <div class="mb-4">
                  <label for="finish_at">모집 종료일</label>
                
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input id="finish_at" />
                        <script>
                            $('#finish_at').datepicker({
                                uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4'
                            });
                        </script> 
                    </div>
                </div>
                    
               
  

                <script type="text/javascript">
                    $(function () {
                        $('#start').datetimepicker({
                            uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4',
                            iconsLibrary: 'fontawesome',
                            minDate: today,
                            maxDate: function () {
                                return $('#endDate').val();
                            }
                        });
                        $('#finish').datetimepicker({
                            useCurrent: false //Important! See issue #1075
                            uiLibrary: 'bootstrap4',
                            iconsLibrary: 'fontawesome',
                            minDate: function () {
                                return $('#startDate').val();
                            }
                        });
                       
                </script>
                                    
                    
                    
			
			     <hr class="mb-4">
                 <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" type="submit">모임 만들기</button>
			    </form>
			
			    <hr>
			
                <p>자세한 약관이 궁금하신가요? <a href="/#">확인하기</a></p>
			    <p><a href="/">홈으로</a>.</p>

			</div>
		
		</div>
      </main>
	</body>
</html>